column5: Just wanted to know if someone could please tell me what the water levels are like on the Maitland or Bayfield Rivers.  Did the rain yesterday screw them up??

Hey Rolly you got a better chance of winning the lottery than getting any type of river information on this site.  If I knew I would tell ya, you might have better luck on the Grey Bruce board some helpful people over there!
My link   Learn to use this site...wont have to put up with people looking down on you for asking river conditions
just do what I use to do get the number for goderich bait and tackle give them a call they will give you an update.
